{
  "stem": "7546.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something had to happen to-- maybe the gypsies [LAUGHS] got me or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was five or six years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know how to get home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was terrified of being in a cemetery with a lot of stones all around me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked out from the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know which way to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walked for about three or four hours, crying terribly, till another policeman stopped me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, why are you crying?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you go home?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told him, I just don't know how to get home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somehow or other, while I was afraid of policemen, this one happened to be a nice man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took me by the hand, he took-- went with me to the precinct, and from the precinct, they took a [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A [POLISH] is a horse with a carriage, and they took me home crying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I told them where I lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just didn't tell them that I know how to get home myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they made my father pay for the [POLISH] and also pay for the [POLISH] for the policeman to go back to his precinct.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was actually my first encounter with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Polish school only for Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a nice building, just a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a lot of schools were in private buildings where people used to live there, tenants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In my case, it was strictly a school that was built by the Jewish agency, but it was strictly for Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Polish school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no other language but Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Jewish, Gentile, and two Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My music teacher was a German, Otto Werner.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
